name: places/ChIJjyZ9dxoa2jERWtj9c5nNS_k/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNYMDd6WG93RRAB
text: {'text': "This place is a gem!! It's fascinating to see the works of botanical artists across time from the British explorers to locals in recent years. They are so technical and intricate. Left feeling struck by the biodiversity in the region and more appreciative of the efforts to study and conserve it. The building itself is also beautiful and peaceful. I really enjoyed my visit!", 'languageCode': 'en'}

name: places/ChIJjyZ9dxoa2jERWtj9c5nNS_k/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURfNmJxQ3d3RRAB
text:
{'text': "Third hike of 2025 after a busy couple of weeks, and it was a pre-Lunar New Year hike @Gallop Extension!

Being underutilised and under-visited, Gallop Extension was an amazingly quiet place. I went straight to the place once I arrived at Nassim Gate and I was not disappointed! The highlights of Gallop Extension included:

(1) OCBC Arboretum
(2) Forest Discovery Centre
(3) COMO Adventure Grove
(4) Botanical Art Gallery
(5) Mingxin Foundation Rambler's Ridge
(6) HPL Canopy Link

So there were many things to see and experience at one go!

Here are some photos of the Botanical Art Gallery.", 'languageCode': 'en'}
